channel.title: UNI-CheatClient [updated AZN-CLIENT]
channel.description:
Remember the good old AZN-cheatclient? Well, we took it, updated it, added some new features, added new cache and models, and now it will work with all servers below 508.
[b]Features[/b] -Manually add fake packets to sent to server (some are build-in)! [i]so its includes: easy dung armor, easy barrows, easy skilling (on some servers), and so on[/i] -Open any interface (manually or choose one from the build-in ones) -Standard, good old AZN features (fake crown, noclip, phats (doesn't work on most servers), and so on.
Tested with -most versions of InisidiaX -most versions of TrisidiaX -almost all old sources
[b]Download:[/b] http://ge.tt/2ghNcYJi/v/0?c
